<scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
<head>Scope and Content
</head>
<p>This is an oath of office for the sheriff of Braxton County [West Virginia]. The oath is also signed by Francis H. Pierpont, governor of the Restored Government of Virginia. On an interesting note, the signer must swear that they hadn't partaken in any dueling. 
</p>
